      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Establishes the Hawaii Lottery and Gaming Corporation for the purpose of conducting and regulating wagering and gaming in the State.  Establishes the Lottery and Gaming Special Fund and allocates certain percentages of the fund to various community betterment purposes."
